Name: Suspicious Blubbercream
Desc: Aqua-blue ice cream. The large chunks of sea salt ambushed your taste buds, causing you to blank out... By the time you mustered up the valor to try again, the dessert had melted into more of a milkshake...
Effect: Increases all party members' DEF by 215 and healing effects by 6% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
